{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Russian was my-- almost my native language.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I didn't know what to do, whether to respond.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I saw that a woman came with a pile of cloth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she start there-- in the little river, she started to wash them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I came out, and I was so hungry that I felt that I put my life in my hands.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I responded to her in Russian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I asked her-- she, first, she was shocked when she saw me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'm sure I looked like a devil, not like a person, you know, at that time, because, you know, from the all day long and from being there on the ground.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I explained to her that I am Jewish and that I'm hungry, and that I'm trying to reach the forest, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she told me that this is a concentration camp, but not a watch camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was from civilians, from civilian Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she told me that they have few Russian POWs who are hiding in the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they also are getting ready to join the freedom fighters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in meantime, she told-- I told her I'm hungry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She told me in a few minutes, she's going to be back and bring me something to eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I figured one of the two.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Either she's going to turn me in, or she's going to bring.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "About half an hour later, she came and had a bottle of milk, a piece of bread, black bread, and a piece of meat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she gave to me-- and this was something to me like-- after two days not having anything to eat, I mean, it was really very rewarding.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She told me also something interesting.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
